      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Kilkivan. ¶ Queensland. ¶ Jan 5th/94. ¶ Baron Sir Ferd. von Mueller, K.C.M.G. ¶ &amp;c. &amp;c. &amp;c....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">94.01.05</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Sophie Hooker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS 443/D, Archives and Manuscripts, Hocken Library, University of Otago, Dunedin, NZ.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Kilkivan.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Queensland.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Jan 5th/94.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Sir Ferd. von Mueller, K.C.M.G.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">&amp;c. &amp;c. &amp;c.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Baron,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I hope you will not be anoyed at my writing thus to you — I am Brian Hookers<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Brian was the son of Joseph Hooker.</p>
               </note> wife, but I cannot hope that you remember me —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My letter is to beg the aid of your influence in trying to procure an appointment for my husband.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>He has been most unfortunate, &amp; is still in New Zealand. He has been there for the last fourteen months, and cannot get back. He has not been idle, it is true; but his Salary was exceedingly small, and he has been compelled to take the last month or so out in shares in the Co[y], because it is short of money &amp; cannot pay.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am afraid it is quite impossible to get an appointment unless one has someone of influence to speak for one. May I ask you, dear Baron, to do that for him? — for the sake of your old friendship for his father.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I dread asking, but one must move if one must live; and I dare not ask anyone else. I have others, too, to think of beside myself.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I know how difficult it is to procure anything, but if you were only to speak on his behalf I am sure that it would benefit him.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M wrote seeking a position in Tasmania for Brian Hooker, but without success; see M to J. Hooker, 18 June 1894<seg style="font-weight: bold; ">. </seg>Brian eventually found a position on the goldfields in WA; see M to J. Hooker, 5 August 1894 and 2 March 1896.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sincerely asking your pardon for so troubling you.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Believe me</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My dear Baron,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours faithfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sophie Hooker.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotations by M: 'Kilkivan.' and 'Rec and answ 13/1/94.' Letter not found.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
